{"tid":996504,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"法國連登仔好撚鍾意扮高尚與別不同😂😂😂","createTime":"2019-01-26T10:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T05:57:06.000Z","uid":218575,"like":63,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"115d8aea4ffb7665b169d2b6f33b8b0ddac5b2c2","tid":996504,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:45:38.000Z","msg":"成日講邊間好食 <br />\n就話呢幾年差咗啦 <br />\n以前仲好食 十足十個老屎忽咁 <br />\n當中有幾多個真係分得出道有無變<br />\n定只係想扮眾人皆醉 唯我獨醒心照啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其次係一講香港邊間野食好食<br />\n又會沖出黎講 食開屎 邊間邊間仲好食啦<br />\n好似拉麵咁 基本上全香港無邊間係無俾人彈<br />\n有啲又話咩日本邊間仲好食啦 <br />\n戇撚柒鳩 咁你咪每次想食<br />\n咪都買張機票過去日本食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n硬係有人懶係自己係食家 <br />\n覺得人地食嘅係屎 自己食過就最正咁 <br />\n好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695729ef19a1168305d2be3233c909e87beb57a9","tid":996504,"uid":42046,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:48:48.000Z","msg":"基本上大部分香港人都出現呢個現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8bcf475b9cb6d9b502911c4187dda963177499","tid":996504,"uid":218575,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"695729ef19a1168305d2be3233c909e87beb57a9","tid":996504,"uid":42046,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:48:48.000Z","msg":"基本上大部分香港人都出現呢個現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:57:54.000Z","msg":"味道不嬲好主觀 但唔否認有啲客觀條件<br />\n有啲極端例子真係好難食 <br />\n例如極咸 唔熟 蒸魚過曬時間等等<br />\n但一間正正常常嘅食店<br />\n都俾佢地吹到點垃圾真係笑死<br />\n<br />\n好似前排有個點心po咁  <br />\n話乜外國點心好食過香港好啲 <br />\n仲放曬相話燒賣大大粒好正 <br />\n咩有料嘅師傅去曬外國 <br />\n講到香港班點心佬一文不值<br />\n又叫人去外國食過再講<br />\n第一 大粒就叫好食 <br />\n咁某位youtuber成日做嘅放大版野食<br />\n一定最撚好食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef6895a4a9c0e6346d3da7fa9d15f90cd9a964e","tid":996504,"uid":68457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T11:32:05.000Z","msg":"仲有一個重點<br />\n同一間餐廳未必任何時間keep到同一水準<br />\n又可能某日個廚請假，又或者廚師突然失手，水準變得好唔同"},{"pid":"a8abf8acacb25523ffeab7ab82151d3555c5a8bf","tid":996504,"uid":186844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:56:31.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係 信佢地真係全港全部餐廳唔使食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53202fb55b83dbbf034eab1471311ef5122d684f","tid":996504,"uid":68457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a8abf8acacb25523ffeab7ab82151d3555c5a8bf","tid":996504,"uid":186844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:56:31.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係 信佢地真係全港全部餐廳唔使食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:18:05.000Z","msg":"蓮燈飲食台最常出現reply (唔計同百狸香有關嘅reply)係鬧人食開屎、狗都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6cd10b66b8dbaddb0da24dbd67c7590c59ba003","tid":996504,"uid":36857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:20:07.000Z","msg":"講拉麵真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n永遠淨係識講邊間垃圾，又唔講覺得邊間好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738fc6fa2b01cd768093e5947361152d146424a7","tid":996504,"uid":133519,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"幾靚女都話係豬西<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 現實原來自己係金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d48e0594cd148af1001f429904f9092c072c73","tid":996504,"uid":75196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:37:29.000Z","msg":"連登仔個個食神，乜撚野都話狗也不屌"},{"pid":"1cffbea9ba88e95e4376814bd0c8ba49cdd6ee65","tid":996504,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:51:32.000Z","msg":"連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2424b6e68db4262b09ff23200824befb2dd7aa66","tid":996504,"uid":218575,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f6cd10b66b8dbaddb0da24dbd67c7590c59ba003","tid":996504,"uid":36857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:20:07.000Z","msg":"講拉麵真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n永遠淨係識講邊間垃圾，又唔講覺得邊間好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"因為佢地驚講咗一間出黎 <br />\n會俾其他食家話垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0200b22846c9274db27ac7f9c34e0f46515a87","tid":996504,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8abf8acacb25523ffeab7ab82151d3555c5a8bf","tid":996504,"uid":186844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:56:31.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係 信佢地真係全港全部餐廳唔使食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"其實理性講下邊到唔好食<br />\n例如太咸太淡太生咁無問題<br />\n好多係一句食開屎 <br />\n又講唔出實際人地野食有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3951ba3207b7153669d18a76235a4f7d81ae5f","tid":996504,"uid":229549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T15:05:30.000Z","msg":"香港人都係咁架啦，成日話邊間重好食，屌你另一間重好食關眼前這間好唔好食咩事？"},{"pid":"2ea959c13679d67a00dff335176d29d1c55dd551","tid":996504,"uid":126569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T15:42:41.000Z","msg":"高登重好睇啦"},{"pid":"1b1c9a893023be5da0ecd70fe288d8d00a198afc","tid":996504,"uid":174420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T15:43:32.000Z","msg":"你咁清高不如講下邊間好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\"